quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  8,53,"Saa na εteε, efirisε, Nyankopͻn nsesa adom bi a Ɔde ama amanfoͻ bi gyesε wͻn ara sesa no. Nokorε sε Nyankopͻn ne Otiefoͻ a Ɔte biribiara, Ɔne Onimdefoͻ a Ɔnim biribiara."
  8,54,"Wͻtesε Farao nkorͻfoͻ no, ne wͻn a wͻdii wͻn anim kan no. Wͻfaa wͻn Wura Nyankopͻn Nsεm no atorͻsεm, enti Yεde wͻn bͻne no sεee wͻn. Yεmaa nsuo faa Farao nkorͻfoͻ. Na wͻn nyinaa yε abͻneεfoͻ."
  8,55,"Nokorε sε, abͻdeε bͻne wͻ Nyankopͻn anim ne wͻn a wͻyi boniayε na wͻnnye (Nyankopͻn Nsεm no) nnie."
  8,56,"(Nkͻmhyεni), wͻn a wone wͻn yε apam a aberε biara wͻbu wͻn apam no soͻ no, wͻnsuro Nyame."
  8,57,"Enti sε wodi wͻn so nkonim wͻ ͻkoo mu a, twe wͻn aso papaapa na fa pamo wͻn a wͻwͻ wͻn akyire no, sεdeε wͻde bεyε afutuo."
  8,58,"(Nkͻmhyεni), sε wonya suro wͻ amanfoͻ bi ho sε wͻbɛdi wo hwammͻ a, to (wͻn apam no) san ma wͻn (wͻ nhyehyεε) pa so, efirisε Nyankopͻn mpε wͻn a wͻdi hwammͻ no asεm."
  8,59,"Ɛmma wͻn a wͻyi (Nyankopͻn Asεm no ho) boniayε no adwen nyε wͻn sε wͻbɛtumi asan (Yεn ho), nokorε sε wͻntumi mma (Nyankopͻn nhyehyεε) nyε kwa."
  8,60,"Monfa apͻnkͻ a yεde kͻ koo (ne atuo ne akodeε ahodoͻ biara) a moahoͻden bɛtumi nyε ahoboa ntwεn wͻn, mfa mmͻ Nyankopͻn atamfoͻ ne moatamfoͻ no ne wͻn a wͻka wͻn ho no hu; monnim wͻn, Nyankopͻn na Ɔnim wͻn. Biribiara a mobɛyi de ama wͻ Nyankopͻn kwan soͻ no, Yεbɛtua no pεpεεpε ama mo, na Yɛnsisi mo."
  8,61,"Sε wͻdane wͻn ho kͻ asomdwoeε so a, dane woho kͻ so bi, na fa wo ho to Nyankopͻn so, nokorε sε, Ɔne Otiefoͻ a Ɔte biribiara no, Ɔne Onimdefoͻ no."
